Let this Christmas Eve be the most delicious one yet with a lavish spread that awaits you on December 24th at the Christmas Eve Dinner. Work up an appetite for everything from roasts, pies, puddings and all the trimmings. The festive dinner at Keraleeyam, Raviz Kadavu will be offered at a special rate of Rs.1200/- plus taxes.
